{
  "stem": "9156.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't understand why that baby couldn't get the nipple getting her orange juice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I realized that I hadn't strained the orange juice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that's very bad, and I have to tell that about myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I finally thought about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that was only a short time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then for quite awhile I got a fine job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got $8 a week for 12 hours of work every day, with the exception of Sunday.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was in the-- in-- I think it's the Bronx.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where's that big bridge going over?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think it's Bronx.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oakland or the Bronx.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and it was an old man, and I have to wash him, and to put clothes on him, and wash the teeth, which he could take out, and so on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, taking care of that old man, but all day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were all things to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then I realized that he had a son who had sleeping sickness.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was-- the saliva was always coming out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he couldn't eat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was really shocked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I started feeding that one, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And finally I washed him, too, because I just couldn't see that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that was a regular job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But lousy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I spoke French fluently, and then there's this third language now, the English.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had learned English, so I could read English.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In school.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many-- in Germany.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many years earlier.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had learned English so I could to read it, and I could-- but it was not very good.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- people always tell all the bad stories, but I think there's some nice stories.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went the third or second day, I was in New York and I wanted to go somewhere.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
